Privacy policy
This policy is applicable to games-related products or services developed, maintained and operated by LEYO GAME LIMITED and its affiliates.
This policy will help you understand the following:
1.We collect your personal information
2.How do we use your personal information
3.Three, how do we use cookies
4. How do we share, transfer, publicly disclose and store your personal information
5. How do we protect your personal information
6. Your Rights
7. How do we handle children's personal information
8. How to update this policy
9.How to contact us
We understand the importance of personal information to you and will do our best to protect your personal information safely and reliably. We are committed to maintaining your trust in us and protecting your personal information by adhering to the following principles: the principle of consistent rights and responsibilities, the principle of clear purpose, the principle of consent, the principle of least enough, the principle of ensuring security, the principle of subject participation, the principle of openness and transparency, etc. At the same time, we promise that we will take appropriate security measures to protect your personal information according to the mature security standards of the industry.
You acknowledge and acknowledge that you have carefully read and understood all contents of this User Privacy Agreement (" This Privacy Policy "or" This Policy ") before using our products or Services. Please note that we use "bold and black" to write special reminders for sensitive personal information. Before providing us with any personally sensitive information belonging to you and/or your End users, please clearly consider that such provision is appropriate and agree that we may process your and/or your End users' personally sensitive Information for the purposes and in the manner described in this Policy. We will collect and use sensitive personal information about you and/or your end users after obtaining your consent in order to implement the relevant functions provided to you. You may choose not to consent to the collection and use of sensitive personal information about you and/or your end users, but refusing to provide such information may affect the provision of relevant service functions for you.
一.We collect your personal information
Personal information refers to all kinds of information recorded by electronic or other means that can identify the identity of a specific natural person or reflect the activities of a specific natural person alone or in combination with other information.
We will only collect your personal information for the following purposes as described in this Policy:
1. In order to meet the requirements of relevant laws, regulations, policies and relevant authorities, game users shall perform real-name authentication to continue using game services. We will collect your real name identity information, including ID card information, military ID card information and passport information, if you voluntarily provide it. Refusing to provide your real name identity information may result in your inability to log in the game or be restricted in the process of using the game service.
2. In order to store part of the local data generated by game users, we will require you to provide read and write permissions for device storage. If you refuse to provide read and write permission to the device storage, we will not be able to provide you with the game service.
3, in order to mark you as a user and used for account ownership dispute processing, if you use the associated WeChat, QQ login game, we will collect your WeChat, QQ corresponding unique identification, (including WeChat account nickname, head, region and gender, QQ account nickname, head, gender), is used to save your login information, So that you can log in to different devices and share game content easily.
4. In order to ensure your normal use of game services, ensure the normal operation of game service functions, optimize game product experience and guarantee the security of your account, we will collect your personal commonly used equipment information, network identification information and network environment information when you register or use game services. Device name, network type, network operator, operating system, application version number, device model, device manufacturer, IOS AD Identifier (IDFA), International Mobile Equipment Identification (IMEI), Anonymous Device Identifier (OAID), International Mobile Subscriber Identification (IMSI), MAC address.
5, in the process of your use of the game service, we will collect your game log information, including login shop logging, the log, activity log, association journal, upgrade log, make friends, chat logs, so that you can view your game on the client history, at the same time will be used for game operation statistical analysis, customer complaint handling, anti-cheating analysis, And game experience optimization and improvement.
6. When you recharge or pay in the game, we will collect your recharge record, consumption record and other information, so that you can query your transaction record, and provide customer service staff with information to support the settlement of dispute claims in case of transaction disputes. At the same time, in order to protect your property security to the greatest extent, we will collect the equipment information, network identification information and network environment information at the time of payment, so as to identify, re-confirm or block high-risk transactions.
7. In order to ensure the security of your game account and create a fair, healthy and safe game environment, we will collect your game application information, equipment information, network identification information, operating system and process information, network environment information and game crash records, etc. In order to combat the destruction of the game fair environment or interference, damage to the normal game service behavior (such as external cheating, etc.).
8, when you are in the game chat rooms or BBS through text, images, voice, video and other methods to release information or interact with other players, we may collect information about you send the above interactive content, used to pornography, violence, politics, abusive, malicious ads and other inappropriate content filtering and monitoring, to purify the game environment, maintain a healthy Internet environment.
9. When you fail to log in to the game or the page cannot be opened, we will collect your IP address from you in order to troubleshoot the local network and provide you with more targeted game maintenance services.
10. To facilitate you to log in to the game through other devices, we will provide QR code scanning login function (as provided by the game). For this purpose, we will obtain your prior authorization to access the camera of your device. Your refusal to provide the permission to open the camera of the device will not affect our provision of game services for you.
11. In order to improve the security of your in-game tourist account and prevent the loss of game records, we suggest that you bind your in-game tourist account to your mobile phone number and will collect your mobile phone number for this purpose. However, your refusal to provide the game service will not affect your continued use of the game service.
12. Your shipping address and mobile phone number may be collected in order to provide you with the in-kind rewards you have won in the game or activity. If you refuse to provide the game, you will not be affected to continue to use the game service, but you will not be able to receive in-kind rewards.
13. According to relevant laws, regulations and national standards, we may collect and use your personal information without your authorization or consent under the following circumstances:
1) Those directly related to national interests such as national security and national defense security;
2) Those directly related to major public interests such as public safety, public health and public knowledge;
3) Those directly related to criminal investigation, prosecution, trial and execution of judgment;
4) To protect your or other individuals' life, property, reputation and other major legitimate rights and interests, but it is difficult to obtain the consent of the person;
5) The personal information collected is disclosed to the public by you;
6) Collecting personal information from legally disclosed information, such as legal news reports, government information disclosure and other channels;
7) It is necessary to sign and perform the contract according to your requirements;
8) Necessary for the maintenance of the safe and stable operation of the provided products or services, such as the discovery and disposal of faults in the products or services;
9) Other circumstances stipulated by laws and regulations.
14, please you understand, we provide you with the functions and services are constantly updated and development, if a certain function or service is not in the foregoing statement and collected your information, we will have a page announcements, tips, interactive process, site updated privacy policy to explain to you the content of the information collection, the scope and purpose, with the consent of you
How do we use your personal information
We will only use your personal information for the following purposes and purposes as described in this Policy:
1. Provide you with various game services and functions, including basic game functions and customer service.
2. Product problem repair and product optimization:
In order to improve the service experience of game users and solve the bugs that may occur during the use of the game, we will use the log information generated during the use of the game service, including device information, geographical information (without precise positioning), game behavior information, and transaction information. Before analyzing the logs, we will anonymize the above information, and then analyze the user types and corresponding game behaviors as a whole.
3. Internal and external audit:
In order to fulfill the obligations stipulated by laws, regulations and regulatory authorities, we may provide anonymized personal information, equipment information and transaction information to regulatory authorities or audit authorities under the premise of signing confidentiality agreements in the process of supporting various internal and external audits.
If we want to use the information for other purposes not specified in this Policy, we will seek your prior consent.
When we want to use the information collected for a specific purpose for another purpose, we will seek your prior consent.
If it is personal information that is not necessary, you may delete the personal information you have provided or revoke the authorization you have provided to us at any time. If you delete the information or cancel the license, you will not be able to implement some functions of the game, but the basic functions of the game will not be affected.
How do we use cookies
A Cookie is a small piece of text sent to the browser by the website a user visits. It usually contains an identifier, the site name, and some numbers and characters. It helps the browser record information about access activity, such as session information, preferred language, and other Settings. That way, the next time you visit the same site, you'll have a much easier and more useful experience.
We use cookies for a variety of purposes, such as recording user session information, login and operation status, default language configuration, and more. Using cookies will give you a better experience with the services you use.
You agree that we collect and use cookies and that we will not use cookies for any purpose other than those described in this Policy. You can manage or delete cookies based on your preferences. For details, see http://www.aboutcookies.org most web browsers have Cookie management functions, such as the need to learn more about how to change the browser Settings, please visit the official website of the corresponding browser Such as Internet Explorer, Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, Safari, and Opera.
